=== K9 User Club ===
Since 2022, users of the K9 howitzer have held an annual conference consisting of three working group sessions: operation, education, and maintenance. Military officials from participating countries are expected to share their various experiences and expertise gained during K9 operations, as well as to discuss optimal methods for operating the howitzer. Additionally, representatives from the defence industry partners of K9, both from member and non-member countries, attended the meeting to present advanced technologies and explore potential cooperation. The goal is to operate the howitzer at maximum efficiency and to create synergy within the defence industry through collaboration.<ref name="Australia Factory 1">{{cite web|date=2022-02-23|script-title=ko:한화디펜스, 호주 아발론공항에 대규모 자주포 생산시설 부지로 확정...3만2000 m<sup>2</sup> 규모|url=http://www.worktoday.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=22705|access-date=2022-02-23|website=워크투데이|language=ko}}</ref><ref name="Australia Factory 2">{{cite web|date=2022-02-23|script-title=ko:한화디펜스, 호주에 대규모 자주포 생산시설 부지 확정|url=http://www.newslock.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=53398|access-date=2022-02-23|website=뉴스락|language=ko}}</ref>

